## basic library

A comprehensive test library for dartdoc_builder.

This library contains various Dart elements for testing
the Markdown documentation generator.

### Classes from basic

- [MyClass](basic/MyClass/MyClass.md) — A simple class with documentation.
- [Comparable2](basic/Comparable2/Comparable2.md) — A class that overloads operators.
- [StringHelper](basic/StringHelper/StringHelper.md) — A string helper.
- [Point](basic/Point/Point.md) — An immutable 2D point.
- [Box](basic/Box/Box.md) — A generic box that holds a value of type [T].
- [BoundedBox](basic/BoundedBox/BoundedBox.md) — A generic box with a bounded type parameter.
- [Animal](basic/Animal/Animal.md) — A base animal class.
- [Dog](basic/Dog/Dog.md) — A dog that extends [Animal].
- [Labrador](basic/Labrador/Labrador.md) — A Labrador that extends [Dog] and mixes in [Swimmable].
- [AbstractFoo](basic/AbstractFoo/AbstractFoo.md) — An abstract class that cannot be instantiated directly.
- [SealedBar](basic/SealedBar/SealedBar.md) — A sealed class that can only be extended within this library.
- [BaseBaz](basic/BaseBaz/BaseBaz.md) — A base class that can be extended but not implemented.
- [FinalQux](basic/FinalQux/FinalQux.md) — A final class that cannot be extended or implemented.
- [InterfaceQuux](basic/InterfaceQuux/InterfaceQuux.md) — An interface class that can be implemented but not extended.
- [MixinClass](basic/MixinClass/MixinClass.md) — A mixin class that can be used as both a class and a mixin.
- [ThresholdTest](basic/ThresholdTest/ThresholdTest.md) — A class with methods of varying sizes for threshold testing.
